The feedback component provides users with a way of giving feedback without leaving the current task. The form is collapsed within a [details component](/components/details) and rendered within the [footer component](/components/footer) by the [page template](/styles/page-template).

The form submits without refreshing the page and the user is notified of the successful submission of feedback. 

